    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Generally, any thing laid over something else, more specifically a transparent sheet placed over an image, text, map, diagram, or artwork, to form a composite.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
